{"tid":1034372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遷粵養老　64歲婦失蹤　同類個案多　半數未能尋回","createTime":"2019-02-23T21:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T21:15:09.000Z","uid":47714,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e27eb80888b8abede56c0f78e97a25def2ede1e1","tid":1034372,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T21:06:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150730/19237125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150730%2F19237125&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=c08b122d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150730%2F19237125&h=21ad4b7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150730/19237125</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://is.gd/DJQtAN\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FDJQtAN&h=dd4007ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東現有約3萬名養老港人，但求助機制不足令人憂慮。本報接獲港人求助，指在內地養老的64歲母親離奇失蹤近兩周，質疑公安未有積極援助。有協助內地港人的機構指類似事故非個別事件，專家則建議長者家人宜為在內地養老長者申請平安鐘、平安電話等服務，免長者失蹤時無從施救。<br />\n<br />\n失蹤的64歲港婦魏桂燕，7月17日在廣東茂名市失蹤後一直無音訊，入境處稱昨回覆指已向家屬了解事件，並會與駐粵經貿辦事處保持聯繫。入境處稱並沒有在內地失蹤香港長者的統計，但廣州工聯會諮詢服務中心的蕭先生稱，該中心每年都收到數宗港人在內地失蹤的求助個案，其中不少是長者，約一半未能尋回。"},{"pid":"a996d4d57ad517c523096bf39ee098c92b9a1f8f","tid":1034372,"uid":49392,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T21:07:14.000Z","msg":"要投票嗰時就會出現"},{"pid":"22dbb36a0b6b58b885f05a2f6b1b3ab9388cd4c4","tid":1034372,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T21:07:38.000Z","msg":"香港山區肺...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca5097a7b1520c871638877dcde8783abaa562c","tid":1034372,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T21:08:46.000Z","msg":"個仔真係醒目!"},{"pid":"b594fe1f44f5b63a069c28abe0bcfa43d891f739","tid":1034372,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T21:15:09.000Z","msg":"有冇研究研究呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇就唔使研究喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}